{"tid":290493,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] C朗將強勢回歸曼聯！預言「相隔十年再取歐冠英超」","createTime":"2017-06-19T20:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T04:06:04.000Z","uid":28938,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39e53b80d4dda0c3646ca40d6c591a30fa8ed7d6","tid":290493,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:39:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>[突發] C朗將強勢回歸曼聯！預言「相隔十年再取歐冠英超」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/043020_b89c98dc81321aadcd78b4f3b344d92d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F043020_b89c98dc81321aadcd78b4f3b344d92d.jpg&h=33d71b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙官方報章《Nineup》最新消息確認，C朗拿度已透過經理人文迪斯與曼聯達成轉會協議，但未有透露轉會費數字。<br />\n<br />\n在洲際國家盃賽和墨西哥後，C朗拿度於酒店接受報章訪問，談到近日轉會傳聞時，他大方地確認將於暑假後回歸曼聯，相關工作將由經理人文迪斯全盤負責。<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙人指出：「十年前我在曼聯中取得英超與歐聯雙冠王(編按：07/08球季)，那是一個完美的時光；回曼聯的原因是，我想證明十年後的我同樣可以成為冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n記者問到32歲的他會否擔心身體未能適應英超緊湊的節奏，C朗巧妙地回答說：「<span style=\"color: blue;\">這不是適應與否的問題，而是我有沒有企圖心征服英超的問題</span>。請留意，我不是溫室小花（記者問：你是在諷刺美斯嗎？），不不不(C朗尷尬地笑起來)，我只是想說我有不斷進步的能力。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/043253_c588fc7b5b5ba25eed0b6bab28b14889.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F043253_c588fc7b5b5ba25eed0b6bab28b14889.png&h=5b6875cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者相信C朗拿度在英超將繼續有統治級表現，唯一問題是要處理好與摩連奴的關係，畢竟兩人在皇馬期間的合作並不算愉快。"},{"pid":"49aa4870f2d905baf3be0fe4e4638fd7eea4db9f","tid":290493,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6829e748b19bb83c05701af214b87a59f7c854a1","tid":290493,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:44:55.000Z","msg":"剛剛已經訓身曼聯來季雙冠王，輕鬆上車不是夢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905fce478b182dfe153993cb32103757c1c98d42","tid":290493,"uid":712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:49:54.000Z","msg":"nineup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391083ae783e7ab41495d6b790aadf1cfd4eb32a","tid":290493,"uid":2338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:51:33.000Z","msg":"牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990af69c987d4073ac6dda8685b8f431ff6b385b","tid":290493,"uid":30808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nineup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bb19bbe6490eafa2cd8bdd0fd2beecfff01303","tid":290493,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:55:44.000Z","msg":"我郎要去教英超班人什麼叫做踢波"},{"pid":"da37805ac45aa9748b97e2207c58961add07d42e","tid":290493,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T21:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nineup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？每份報紙都會有名"},{"pid":"c5839d81675e65756ec5ede1672f8fd4cee2b028","tid":290493,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T21:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強勢回歸：<br />\n<br />\n球會榮譽<br />\n17/18 英超冠軍暨神射手<br />\n17/18 歐聯冠軍暨神射手<br />\n<br />\n國家隊榮譽<br />\n2017年洲際國家盃冠軍暨神射手<br />\n2018年世界盃冠軍暨神射手"},{"pid":"8553dcdf7730d3f4c88201cfa38abfce1853bbd2","tid":290493,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66ab71457d36a7961118725eaf36a2967d7fab17","tid":290493,"uid":35298,"